"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        MACSignatureKeyInformation structs with different cryptographic
        parameters.
        """
a = objects.MACSignatureKeyInformation(cryptographic_parameters=attributes.
    CryptographicParameters(block_cipher_mode=enums.BlockCipherMode.CBC))
b = objects.MACSignatureKeyInformation(cryptographic_parameters=attributes.
    CryptographicParameters(block_cipher_mode=enums.BlockCipherMode.GCM))
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
